article_title: Hungry Wino In Toronto's Vine Country

article_metadata.description: Everyone says the Canadians are nicer than the rest. Can the same be said about their food and wine? Fathom contributor and dedicated foodie Kate Donnelly recounts a recent delicious weekend in and around The Queen City.
article_metadata.author: Fathom
